name: Anti-Anxiety
0:
”Alexa, open anti anxiety”
”Alexa, ask anti anxiety to read me a quote”
”Alexa, ask anti anxiety to help me”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: anti anxiety
des:
This is for people who easily get anxious, and needs some inspiration/encouragement to help reduce anxiety. When asking Alexa to help you with your anxiety, Alexa will provide you with comforting quotes and phrases that aims to help you calm down. 
DISCLAIMER: This is not a cure for your anxiety, or a replacement for your therapy. This is just to temporarily help you reduce your stress and anxiety by providing you anti-anxiety quotes I've retrieved from the internet. I did not create these quotes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
